置大概是怎么样的呢", "content_rendered": "<p>公司打算上深信服的云桌面,目前开发主要是 java 后端跟 vue 前端,然后每台电脑限制不能上网或者只能上少数几个网站,下载资料只能通过另外的电脑,开发电脑不能上传等等管控.  想问问各位大佬有用过这种东西吗,体验怎么样,开发时容易卡死不,分给每台的配置大概是怎么样的呢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622255503, "replies": 25, "id": 779978}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1621872861", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1621872861", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 11536, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1621872861", "stars": 2052, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"username": "Duccck", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb42/cfc8/77698_mini.png?m=1486957950", "bio": "摇滚迷幻电音爱好者。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Duccck", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1413698868, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb42/cfc8/77698_mini.png?m=1486957950", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb42/cfc8/77698_mini.png?m=1486957950", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 77698}, "last_reply_by": "smallaccount", "last_touched": 1622276077, "title": "想转行前端，面临 3 个选择，向大佬请教", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/779994", "created": 1622260757, "content": "### 个人背景\r\n- 27 岁，本科计算机专业，毕业后没从事编程\r\n### 技术掌握情况\r\n- HTML / CSS / JS / jQuery (会点 PHP 和 MySQL，能捣鼓个简单网站的程度)\r\n- Vue (文档自定义指令之前部分) \r\n- [Github 主页]( https://github.com/duccck)\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n### 目前的 3 个选择\r\n- 继续自学 Vue 全家桶再找工作\r\n- 有个做外包项目的小工作室的实习岗机会\r\n- 找个靠谱培训班系统学习一下再出来找工作\r\n\r\n### 有点迷茫，请各位大佬不吝赐教 :)", "content_rendered": "<h3>个人背景</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>27 岁，本科计算机专业，毕业后没从事编程</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>技术掌握情况</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML / CSS / JS / jQuery (会点 PHP 和 MySQL，能捣鼓个简单网站的程度)</li>\n<li>Vue (文档自定义指令之前部分) </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/duccck\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github 主页</a>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>目前的 3 个选择</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>继续自学 Vue 全家桶再找工作</li>\n<li>有个做外包项目的小工作室的实习岗机会</li>\n<li>找个靠谱培训班系统学习一下再出来找工作</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>有点迷茫，请各位大佬不吝赐教 :)</h3>\n", "last_modified": 1622272297, "replies": 21, "id": 779994}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 14941, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825", "stars": 1825, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "xin1284", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4912/9551/29340_mini.png?m=1352088109", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xin1284", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1352088060, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4912/9551/29340_mini.png?m=1352088109", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4912/9551/29340_mini.png?m=1352088109", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 29340}, "last_reply_by": "zhuangku556", "last_touched": 1622276290, "title": "之前一直想买 HomePod，谁知就停产了！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/779973", "created": 1622254515, "content": "本来价格降到了 1500 左右的全新未激活，都没入手，就等着 HomePod mini 上市后再降一波，没想到这玩意直接停产了，如今买了 apple tv 特别想弄一对 HomePod 组双声道，但是看了下价格涨了好多，所谓的富士康资源机都 1800 了……全新的价格更是让人吐血\r\n\r\n所以想问下各位，所谓的富士康资源机靠谱吗？ HomePod 这种应该很难拆机组装吧，保修不保修不重要，只要没大质量问题就 ok 。", "content_rendered": "<p>本来价格降到了 1500 左右的全新未激活，都没入手，就等着 HomePod mini 上市后再降一波，没想到这玩意直接停产了，如今买了 apple tv 特别想弄一对 HomePod 组双声道，但是看了下价格涨了好多，所谓的富士康资源机都 1800 了……全新的价格更是让人吐血</p>\n<p